/**
 * @copyright Copyright (c) 2026 nsix. All rights reserved.
 *
 * @brief Keyboard input handling.
 *
 * @details This module provides functions for handling keyboard input.
 *
 * @note engine_key_e values are based on scancode (the physical location of the
 * key on the keyboard), not keycode (the character generated by the key press,
 * which can change based on keyboard layout and modifiers).
 *
 * To get the key value of the current keyboard layout, use engine_key_name() or
 * engine_key_name_ex() with the appropriate modifiers.
 */

